bgDescription: Using a solid solvent made by a special process. Just one tablet can put the whole squad in a melodious melody and follow the music to finish the battle gracefully.
description: Grants the selected Resonators in the party 1 Concerto Energy per second for 180 seconds, effective only on your own Resonators in Co-op.
